ContourPath

public ContourPath(ContourAttrib attr,
                   int levelIndex,
                   double[] x,
                   double[] y)
Construct a contour path or line using the given arrays of X & Y values.

Parameters:
attr - Attributes assigned to this contour path.
levelIndex - The index to then level this path belongs to.
x - Array of X coordinate values.
y - Array of Y coordinate values.
